Specifications

FAQ




 VariGuard SmartGlassTM and SmartPlasticTM are the first and only display panels that offer a wide range of visible light transmission, instant switching between dark and clear states, and >99% UV-blocking at all times. Based on patented SPD light-control technology developed by Research Frontiers, VariGuard display panels optimally protect artifacts by limiting their light-exposure only to those times when people are viewing them.
 Applications:
Freestanding, wall and table top display cases
Picture frames
Partitions

 Available with high performance anti-reflection and IR-rejection properties.
VariGuard – the best protection for your light-sensitive artifacts.
    


Visible Light Transmittance:
As low as 99.96% light blockage
As high as 65% light transmission


UV rejection::
As high as 99.9% (full-time), Protection up to 400 nm
As high as 65% light transmission


Solar Control:
Dark state: As high as 95% heat blockage
